item.title: Need help with starting private server
item.dc:creator: @iceyfang iceyfang
item.description:
@iceyfang wrote:

Lord_Chris:

yes it shows error connecting to server. i don’t know what to do to make it allow people to log in…

open your port(43594)
portforward www.portforward.com
go to no-ip.org and create an acc then clic manage, add, and fill in the details (name is your server name without the no-ip.org/info/biz)
then try it.

oh, try logging into your server with the server name as 127.0.0.1 (your personal ip thing)
